Cukup, Vanesa. Pergilah.

985
01:20:34,534 --> 01:20:35,901
Apa maksudmu?

986
01:20:35,902 --> 01:20:38,437
Apa kamu tak ingin tahu
mengapa pemilik terakhir pergi...

987
01:20:38,438 --> 01:20:40,472
tanpa menyelesaikan rumah itu?

988
01:20:40,473 --> 01:20:44,177
Tidak, ini sudah terlalu.
Vanesa, pulanglah.

989
01:20:44,178 --> 01:20:46,145
Sekarang.

990
01:20:52,853 --> 01:20:54,754
Maafkan aku, sob.

991
01:21:17,345 --> 01:21:18,311
Halo.

992
01:21:18,312 --> 01:21:19,912
Rachel?

993
01:21:19,913 --> 01:21:21,014
Dr Livingston?

994
01:21:21,015 --> 01:21:22,848
Saya menelepon
mau tau kabar.

995
01:21:22,849 --> 01:21:24,884
Kamu melewatkan janji
temu terakhir kita.

996
01:21:24,885 --> 01:21:26,886
Memastikan semuanya
baik-baik saja.

997
01:21:26,887 --> 01:21:28,721
Semuanya sempurna.

998
01:21:28,722 --> 01:21:30,924
Benarkah? Itu bagus.

999
01:21:31,292 --> 01:21:32,992
Kami mengikuti saran anda.

1000
01:21:32,993 --> 01:21:34,960
Suamiku mendekorasi
salah satu kamar tidur...

1001
